Subsumption-based Planning over Affordances

The goal achieve complex tasks using potential-based wayfields associated with each constituent atomic motion. A null-space subsumption architecture was used to execute multiple motions while ensuring that any action cannot negatively impact another that has a higher priority.

October 26, 2019
